"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-07-26-paris-olympics-viewing-guide-what-to-watch-each-day\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Summer Olympic Games kick off in Paris, France on Friday, July 26, starting with the opening ceremony that will take place on the Seine River.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999944225237, \"rank\": 5.577473172923893e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9947041862620224, \"rank\": 0.0043674092118987555, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The international competition will highlight 40 different sports - with the notable debut of breaking, better known as break dancing - involving 206 countries from around the world.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the games have already begun, including various soccer matches (football if you are not American), and trying to keep track of every event is a bit overwhelming.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately, we have curated a day-by-day list highlighting some of the most popular events taking place over the next two weeks.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Included are standout American talents like gymnastSimone Biles,100-metersprintersSha'Carri Richardson and Noah Lyles, and swimmer Katie Ledecky.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9760666007160853, \"rank\": 0.024520245318109132, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wiki